reviewText: Love watching the Gilmore girls all over again.  It's been great watching Lorelai and Rory banter back and forth again.  They have a great relationship, that every Mother and daughter should have.

Both Season 3 and Season 4 separate boxes but packaged together. Only downside is there was a sticker combining the two boxes (and it seemed like a very old sticker) that did not come off and ruined the front of the boxes when I tried to carefully remove it. But the DVDs are unopened, great condition. This is an excellent deal as long as you aren't planning on displaying the boxes

There was no picture of this product at the time I ordered it, so I was a little skeptical. However, I received it today and it is indeed Gilmore girls seasons 3 and 4..they were in the combined package wrap just like the Seasons 1 + 2 combo was. The only problem was that there was no package wrap to cushion through the journey, but they arrived undamaged.

Okay, so, Gilmore Girls. You either love it or you hate it and I just cannot get enough. I have watched every episode at least 10 times (no, I'm not a weirdo and yes, I do have a life). Honestly, it can sometimes be a little corny and quirky and the acting could be a bit better and it's getting kind of old now so when I see those beepers, I kind of cringe but it's some of the best writing on TV ever and it's heart-warming and entertaining. It's fast and funny and the characters are loveable and very well-developed. Lorelai, the mom, is funny and quirky and selfish and loving. Rory, the daughter, is smart and booky and kind of cold and sarcastic but very loveable. Their relationship is inappropriate at times but very special. BUY IT! Oh and from one huge fan to ANYONE WHO IS READING.. Please make a movie!
The cover art is grainy & the DVD's sometimes won't play on my brand new computer. Other than that it's fine.

We liked all the episodes we could watch but 2 discs wouldn't work no matter how much we cleaned them. I may take them to a local store to be cleaned by their machine, maybe it will work then. Otherwise we are happy with what we received, they shipped very quickly.
I bought the whole series, Amazon has the best prices I've found on the DVDs.  I love the writing and references to pop culture.  Awesome show!
This is one of my Favorite shows! I love the Gilmore Girls! Stars Hollow would be a great place to live........I would love to find a town like that.
I am  a big Gilmore girl fan so of course I loved it.  The Quality and the packaging is great.
I enjoy watching this tv show because of its quippy dialogue. Same reason I have enjoyed watching Psych. I wish more shows were like these two.
The Gilmore Girls grow on you.  You have to  know what the girls get in and out of in Stars Hollow.
I loved this TV show. I was able to watch the reruns on the weekends. Then the channel that showed it was dropped.  Now I'm back to enjoying it again.

I am very unhappy with my product. I received this thinking that the dvd set was new. I began to open it and saw that the side was crushed. I continued to take it out of the sleeve and all of the plastic was completely broken. The DVDs are all over the place and there are also scratches on a few of the DVDs. I cannot even close them back up. I am not happy. No one deserves to pay for a broken DVD set. I will never order from them again.
The wife loves this show like no other. The things 9yrs old and she watches each season and episode like it just came out yesterday.lol. good program

Gilmore Girls is my favorite show.  I have watched the DVDs so many times.  Witty writing, fantastic actors, and engaging dialogue.  These two seasons are my favorites: Rori's senior year of high school and freshman year of college.
This show is awesome funny and very witty! it was a great price. It was shipped the same day i ordered it and it came within 4 days!
I love Gilmore Girls. The dvds came in perfect condition. No scratches or dings. the price was really affordable as well.

Love the show it is fast paced and very witty. I introduced the first season to my son and daughter at Christmas and they were hooked after the first episode. We watch 2 episodes every night. It will be a sad day when we get to the end.

This double set is exactly as pictured. The disks are in great shape. The interior of the case that holds the disks in place was broken but that didn't affect the disks at all. The price makes up for this small defect.
If you love the Gilmore girls this is your item. Two seasons at a very reasonable price. I was going to order the complete collection but it was cheaper to order all the seasons separate.

Loved them! Arrived undamaged and a slight delay due to weather conditions. I could not wait to catch up on the Gilmore Girls since I have been watching season one for over a month every night (that's the only one I had).
Gilmore Girls will always and forever be hours of light-hearted, hilarious humor than no one can pass up. If you love Gilmore Girls (and you should), you can't go wrong with this buy.

I love Gillmore Girls!!  It was the two seasons I didn't have.
It was a great price and came quickly even with the Christmas rush.
It was a Xmas  gift for my daughter and she was so excited....she already had seasons 1 and 2...still have the rest to get.
Gilmore Girls is one of my daughter's favorite shows and these movies have been a great addition to her collection. They arrived in perfect shape!

I indeed received the Gilmore Girls seasons 3 &4. All 12 discs are in perfect condition and so is the box for season 4. The plastic case for season 3, however, is a shambles. It was cracked in so many little pieces and the component that holds the discs had come loose. It's fine, I didn't need the box, but it would have been nice to have the option.
This product is advertised as season 3 and 4 but I only received season 4....super lame....it will be returned pronto!
I love the show and it arrived on time, which is an added bonus! The combo of seasons was a great idea... now if the 6th season would become more reasonably priced...
I'm so excited to get my Gilmore Girls DVD's at a great price! Can't wait to have the whole series!
GREAT PRODUCT I BOUGHT FOR MY DAUGHTER FOR HER BIRTHDAY.  WE LOVE ALL THE GILMORE GIRLS AND SHE COULDN'T BE HAPPIER.

The show is fantastic. If you're reading this review at all, you probably already know that. Its a bummer, though, that none of the seasons are available in any aspect ratio other than 1.33:1. Its weird watching something square(ish) on TVs these days.

What a great deal I was looking to start my collection on these DVDs and found this two pack.
I got it fast and cheaper than buying separate. I'm very happy! When I took it out of the packaging looks
Like I bought two separate items. I'm hopping there are more two pack of other seasons. This will save me lots of money.
